This Is the document for more of the artistic outline of what the game should be.

The Game will be about conquistadors exploring south america in the 1600s.
This will be exploring deserts jungles and mountains that are interesting in the region but also having some more fantastical elements to 
highten the already ritch cultural foundations. This brings the game into more of a historical fantasy genre.

